  "title": "F&B Executive",
  "description": "<p>The applicant would be tasked on the following:</p>\n<p>- Handling prep work in the Restaurant which include preparing bread, preparing protein and vegetables.</p>\n<p>- Handling cashier in the Restaurant</p>\n<p>- Handling Quality Assurance, Service Excellence and tip top cleanliness in the Restaurant</p>\n<p>- Perform opening shift in the Restaurant</p>\n<p>- Perform closing shift in the Restaurant</p>\n<p>- Aid the Operations / Area Manager in meeting scheduling needs</p>\n<p>- Ensuring audit checks are performed regularly which specifically include food safety checks</p>\n<p>- Keep morale of the employee high</p>\n<p>- Manage Labour Cost in the Restaurant</p>\n<p>- Manage Food Cost in the Restaurant</p>\n<p>- Team player</p>\n<p>- Highly self motivated</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Weekend and Weeknights commitment are required.</p>",
